{"lemma":"مَرْفُوع","slug":"مَرْفُوع","root":"ر.ف.ع","root_slug":"ر-ف-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ف-ع","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مَرْفُوع","root":"رفع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n16174"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D9%81%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%B9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"elevated, raised, uplifted"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"nominative case","tags":["nominative"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"indicative mood"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"a statement or action from a hadith narration attributed to the prophet Muhammad by a contemporary companion"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the passive participle of رَفَعَ (rafaʕa, “raise up”): literally, “raised up”."},"ipa":["/mar.fuːʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n16174","headword_ar":"مَرْفُوعٌ","root":"rfE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"pass. part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafaEahu","text_ar":"رَفَعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wafuru$K marofuwEapK","text_ar":"وَفُرُشٍ مَرْفُوعَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, *) in the Kur [lvi. 32], (S,) means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And beds raised"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one upon another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, S, Bd, K:) or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of high estimation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd:) or (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"brought near"},{"kind":"text","text":"to them: (S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wives elevated"},{"kind":"text","text":"upon couches: (Bd:) or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honoured wives."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadiyvN","text_ar":"حَدِيثٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marofuwEN","text_ar":"مَرْفُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A tradition related by a Companion of the Prophet, and ascribed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attributed, to the Prophet himself, by the mention of him as its author,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"persons, up to the Prophet, by whom it has been handed down."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kull p. 152.)       -A2-  It is also an inf. n.: [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafaEa","text_ar":"رَفَعَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaEiyru","text_ar":"البَعِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the latter half of the first paragraph:] and signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain pace"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a beast, (S, TA,) of a horse and of a camel; (L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawoDuwEN","text_ar":"مَوْضُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxofuwDN","text_ar":"مَخْفُوضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xfD","text_ar":"خفض"},{"kind":"text","text":";) it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a run below that termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuDor","text_ar":"حُضْر"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above that which is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawoDuwE","text_ar":"مَوْضُوع"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and below that which is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eadow","text_ar":"عَدْو"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA: [but probably"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Edw","text_ar":"عدو"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuDor","text_ar":"حُضْر"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pace"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rising above the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy and quick rate of going termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hamolajap","text_ar":"هَمْلَجَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (ISk.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layosa","text_ar":"لَيْسَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu marofuwEN","text_ar":"لَهُ مَرْفُوعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a beast)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has not the pace termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mrfwE","text_ar":"مرفوع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Fr","Bd","K","TA"]}]}}